Title: Setting Your Very Own Net
Description: Want to try out your net? Go to the river mouth to the south of Waking Shores, and find a place where the fish are abundant. There should be a good spot for setting up a net.
ObjectivesText: Set up a fishing net in the River Mouth Fishing Hole.
RewardText: Good. Don't forget to pick up your fishing net in a few hours. We don't want the fish to go to waste!
